description: Fresh Off the Truck is an Austin-based mobile food truck that specializes in creating Asian street food. Our purpose, passion, and inspiration is to serve, share, and discover about authentic flavors from the far East that will make you feel as if you were fresh off the boat. Aside from our menus, we here at Fresh Off the Truck would love to hear from you our fellow trucketeers! Tell us all about your favorite Asian Street Food memories and we will try to recreate that oh-so tasteful feeling and feature your request as our Special Treat of the Day. We look forward to serving the streets of Austin! Keep Tuned for upcoming updates!Ni-Haowdy again ATX and Happy Eatings!
name: Fresh off the Truck
